response.overview: The life of a Russian physician and poet who, although married to another, falls in love with a political activist's wife and experiences hardship during World War I and then the October Revolution.
response.tagline: Turbulent were the times and fiery was the love story of Zhivago, his wife and the passionate, tender Lara.
response.title: Doctor Zhivago
